{
  "info": {
    "name": "CampusWork API",
    "description": "Complete API test collection for CampusWork — a part-time job system for university students.\n\n## How to use\n1. Import this file into Postman\n2. Set the `base_url` variable to `http://127.0.0.1:8000`\n3. Run requests in the order they appear — Auth first, then by role\n4. Tokens are saved automatically after login",
